    Thanks Brice,<br>
    <br>
    bottom line, even if hwloc is not fully ported, it should build and
    ompi should get something usable.<br>
    in this case, i have no objection removing the --without-hwloc
    configure option.<br>
    <br>
    you can contact me off-list regarding the FX10 specific issue<br>
    <br>
    Cheers,<br>
    <br>
    Gilles<br>
    <br>
